OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773648269
OL,3,CLabour MPs urge prime minister to save
OL,4,Cthe assisted dying bill
OL,6,FConservative, Liberal Democrat, Green,
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru and Reform MPs have also
OL,8,Fwritten separate letters to the prime
OL,9,Fminister, bringing the total number of
OL,10,Fconcerned MPs to around 150.
OL,12,FThe Terminally Ill Adults (End of
OL,13,FLife) Bill still has four days left of
OL,14,Fdebate in the House of Lords, but both
OL,15,Fsupporters and opponents now believe
OL,16,Fthat won't be enough to get through
OL,17,Fthe remainder of the more than 1,200
OL,18,Famendments peers have proposed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773648269
OL,3,CLabour MPs urge prime minister to save
OL,4,Cthe assisted dying bill
OL,6,FDespite 11 days of debate on the
OL,7,Famendments so far, only half of them
OL,8,Fhave so far been discussed.
OL,10,FIf the bill runs out of time it will
OL,11,Ffail to pass in this session of
OL,12,Fparliament, despite being approved in
OL,13,Ftwo separate votes by MPs.
OL,15,FThere have been accusations that a
OL,16,Fhandful of peers are deliberately
OL,17,Ftrying to run down the clock, or
OL,18,Ffilibuster, in order to ensure that
OL,19,Fthe bill fails.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773648269
OL,3,CLabour MPs urge prime minister to save
OL,4,Cthe assisted dying bill
OL,6,FHowever, the bill's opponents insist
OL,7,Fit is a flawed bill which requires
OL,8,Fdetailed scrutiny and amendment.
OL,10,FNow a joint letter from Labour MPs has
OL,11,Fbeen coordinated by Peter Prinsley, a
OL,12,Fconsultant doctor and MP for Bury St
OL,13,FEdmunds and Stowmarket, urging the
OL,14,Fprime minister to intervene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
