PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773648269
OL,3,CLabour MPs urge prime minister to save
OL,4,Cthe assisted dying bill
OL,6,FThere are also some other, less
OL,7,Fconventional routes, such as what's
OL,8,Fknown as a ten minute rule bill or a
OL,9,Fpresentation bill, but these options
OL,10,Fare less tested and would require a
OL,11,Fmore unusual intervention from the
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
